<h1 id="the-nuts-and-bolts-and-crystals-of">THE NUTS AND BOLTS (AND CRYSTALS) OF</h1>
<h1 id="scintillator-technology">SCINTILLATOR TECHNOLOGY</h1>
<p><em>by <strong>David Brown</strong></em> <em>building on work by Paul Schotanus</em></p>
<p><strong>Berkeley Nucleonics Corporation</strong></p>
<p><em>SECOND EDITION - EXPANDED &amp; UPDATED</em></p>
